title: The Ten Best Moments of the 2023 Men's ODI World Cup
description: On the ten-year anniversary of the first ever episode of the show, Cat and Dan are back to cover the highlights from the last week of cricket. Topics include: Meg Lanning's retirement The Top Ten Moments of the World Cup Cat's Gambling Corner Plus, another thrilling Muller Award Pre-order Dan's new book, The 100 Funniest Moments in Australian Cricket at liebcricket.com/100funniest Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
author: Dan Liebke, Cat Jones
